Class Mini2DxMockGraphics

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.badlogic.gdx.backends.headless.mock.graphics.MockGraphics

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.badlogic.gdx.Graphics

    public class Mini2DxMockGraphics
extends com.badlogic.gdx.backends.headless.mock.graphics.MockGraphics
    libgdx: The headless backend does its best to mock elements. This is intended to make code-sharing between server and client as simple as possible. extending: return value for getFramesPerSecond() added sleepTillDeltaTime making use of updateTime values
